prediction.sparql:
PREFIX fb: <http://rdf.freebase.com/ns/>
SELECT ?collegeTeam ?collegeTeamName WHERE {
  fb:m.095xk6 fb:people.person.education ?educationEntity .
  ?educationEntity fb:education.education.institution ?collegeTeam .
  ?collegeTeam fb:type.object.name ?collegeTeamName .
  FILTER ( ?collegeTeam = fb:m.01vs5c )
}

PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#>
PREFIX fb: <http://rdf.freebase.com/ns/>
SELECT ?draft_year WHERE {
  ?draft_pick fb:sports.sports_league_draft_pick.draftee fb:m.097yk7 .
  ?draft_pick fb:sports.sports_league_draft_pick.draft ?draft_event .
  ?draft_event fb:common.topic.description ?description .
  BIND( xsd:integer ( substr( str( ?description ) , 1 , 4 ) ) AS ?draft_year )
}
LIMIT 1

PREFIX fb: <http://rdf.freebase.com/ns/>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
SELECT DISTINCT ?character ?characterName WHERE {
  ?performance fb:tv.regular_tv_appearance.actor fb:m.021yw7 ; fb:tv.regular_tv_appearance.series fb:m.019nnl ; fb:tv.regular_tv_appearance.character ?character ; fb:tv.regular_tv_appearance.special_performance_type fb:m.02nsjvf .
  ?character rdfs:label ?characterName .
  FILTER ( LANG( ?characterName ) = "en" )
}

PREFIX fb: <http://rdf.freebase.com/ns/>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
SELECT ?actor ?actorName WHERE {
  fb:m.02qd_td fb:film.film_character.portrayed_in_films ?performance .
  ?performance fb:film.performance.actor ?actor .
  ?actor rdfs:label ?actorName .
  FILTER ( LANG( ?actorName ) = "en" )
}

PREFIX fb: <http://rdf.freebase.com/ns/>
SELECT DISTINCT ?team ?teamName WHERE {
  fb:m.0443c fb:sports.pro_athlete.teams ?roster .
  ?roster fb:sports.sports_team_roster.team ?team .
  ?team fb:type.object.name ?teamName .
  FILTER ( LANG( ?teamName ) = "en" )
}

PREFIX fb: <http://rdf.freebase.com/ns/>
SELECT ?final ?startDate WHERE {
  fb:m.0j6tr fb:sports.sports_team.championships ?final .
  ?final fb:type.object.name ?name .
  ?final fb:time.event.start_date ?startDate .
  FILTER ( CONTAINS( LCASE( ?name ) , "stanley cup finals" ) )
}
ORDER BY DESC ( ?startDate )
LIMIT 1

PREFIX fb: <http://rdf.freebase.com/ns/>
SELECT DISTINCT ?wifeName WHERE {
  fb:m.018fzs fb:people.person.spouse_s ?marriage .
  ?marriage fb:people.marriage.spouse ?wife .
  ?wife fb:type.object.name ?wifeName .
  FILTER ( ?wife != fb:m.018fzs )
}

PREFIX fb: <http://rdf.freebase.com/ns/>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
SELECT ?composition ?compositionLabel WHERE {
  fb:m.01vvy fb:music.composer.compositions ?composition .
  ?composition rdfs:label ?compositionLabel .
  FILTER ( LANG( ?compositionLabel ) = "en" )
}

PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#>
PREFIX fb: <http://rdf.freebase.com/ns/>
SELECT DISTINCT ?year WHERE {
  fb:m.09b6zr fb:government.politician.election_campaigns ?campaign .
  ?campaign fb:type.object.name ?name .
  FILTER ( CONTAINS( LCASE( ?name ) , "presidential campaign" ) ) BIND( xsd:int ( REPLACE( STR( ?name ) , ".*([0-9]{4}).*" , "$1" ) ) AS ?year )
}
ORDER BY ?year

PREFIX fb: <http://rdf.freebase.com/ns/>
SELECT ?draftYear WHERE {
  fb:m.012xdf fb:sports.drafted_athlete.drafted ?draft .
  ?draft fb:sports.sports_league_draft_pick.draft ?draftEvent .
  ?draftEvent fb:sports.sports_league_draft.year ?draftYear .
}
LIMIT 1

PREFIX fb: <http://rdf.freebase.com/ns/>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
SELECT ?county ?countyLabel WHERE {
  fb:m.013nm2 fb:location.location.containedby ?county .
  ?county rdfs:label ?countyLabel .
  FILTER ( LANG( ?countyLabel ) = "en" && CONTAINS( ?countyLabel , "County" ) )
}

PREFIX fb: <http://rdf.freebase.com/ns/>
SELECT ?actor ?actorName ?character ?characterName WHERE {
  fb:m.01b64v fb:tv.tv_program.regular_cast ?performance .
  ?performance fb:tv.regular_performance.actor ?actor .
  ?performance fb:tv.regular_performance.character ?character .
  ?character fb:type.object.name ?characterName .
  ?actor fb:type.object.name ?actorName .
}
LIMIT 50

PREFIX fb: <http://rdf.freebase.com/ns/>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
SELECT ?locationName WHERE {
  fb:m.01ymq1 fb:location.location.containedby ?location .
  ?location rdfs:label ?locationName
  FILTER ( lang( ?locationName ) = "en" )
}
LIMIT 1

PREFIX fb: <http://rdf.freebase.com/ns/>
SELECT DISTINCT ?participant ?participantName WHERE {
  fb:m.0c6qh fb:base.popstra.celebrity.dated ?dated .
  ?dated fb:base.popstra.dated.participant ?participant .
  ?participant fb:type.object.name ?participantName .
  FILTER ( LANG( ?participantName ) = "en" )
}

PREFIX fb: <http://rdf.freebase.com/ns/>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
SELECT ?partyLabel WHERE {
  fb:m.0gzh fb:government.politician.party ?partyTenure .
  ?partyTenure fb:government.political_party_tenure.party ?party .
  ?party rdfs:label ?partyLabel .
  FILTER ( LANG( ?partyLabel ) = "en" )
}

PREFIX fb: <http://rdf.freebase.com/ns/>
SELECT DISTINCT ?senator ?name ?govBodyName WHERE {
  fb:m.0b_chkn fb:government.government_office_or_title.office_holders ?position .
  ?position fb:government.government_position_held.office_holder ?senator .
  ?senator fb:type.object.name ?name .
  ?position fb:government.government_position_held.jurisdiction_of_office fb:m.05kkh .
  ?position fb:government.government_position_held.governmental_body ?govBody .
  ?govBody fb:type.object.name ?govBodyName .
  FILTER ( LANG( ?name ) = "en" ) FILTER ( LANG( ?govBodyName ) = "en" ) OPTIONAL {
    ?position fb:base.schemapatterns.time_mediation_schema_pattern.end ?end
  }
  FILTER ( ! BOUND( ?end ) )
}
LIMIT 10

PREFIX fb: <http://rdf.freebase.com/ns/>
SELECT DISTINCT ?actor ?actorName WHERE {
  ?character fb:type.object.name "Éowyn" @en .
  ?character fb:film.film_character.portrayed_in_films ?performance .
  ?performance fb:film.performance.actor ?actor .
  ?actor fb:type.object.name ?actorName .
  ?performance fb:film.performance.film ?film .
  ?film fb:type.object.name ?filmName .
  FILTER ( CONTAINS( LCASE( ?filmName ) , "lord of the rings" ) )
}

PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#>
PREFIX fb: <http://rdf.freebase.com/ns/>
SELECT DISTINCT ?year WHERE {
  fb:m.01d6g fb:sports.sports_team.championships ?worldSeries .
  ?worldSeries fb:type.object.name ?name .
  ?worldSeries fb:time.event.start_date ?startDate .
  BIND( year( xsd:dateTime ( ?startDate ) ) AS ?year ) FILTER ( CONTAINS( LCASE( ?name ) , "world series" ) )
}
ORDER BY ?year

PREFIX fb: <http://rdf.freebase.com/ns/>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
SELECT DISTINCT ?actor ?actorLabel WHERE {
  fb:m.07h5g6 fb:tv.tv_series_episode.guest_stars ?performance .
  ?performance fb:tv.tv_episode_performance.character fb:m.035szd .
  ?performance fb:tv.tv_episode_performance.actor ?actor .
  ?actor rdfs:label ?actorLabel .
}

PREFIX fb: <http://rdf.freebase.com/ns/>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
SELECT ?country ?countryLabel WHERE {
  fb:m.09889g fb:people.person.place_of_birth ?placeOfBirth .
  ?placeOfBirth ( fb:location.location.containedby ) * fb:m.09c7w0 .
  fb:m.09c7w0 rdfs:label ?countryLabel .
  FILTER ( LANG( ?countryLabel ) = "en" ) BIND( fb:m.09c7w0 AS ?country )
}
LIMIT 1

PREFIX fb: <http://rdf.freebase.com/ns/>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
SELECT DISTINCT ?position ?positionLabel WHERE {
  fb:m.02d9k fb:soccer.football_player.position_s ?position .
  ?position rdfs:label ?positionLabel .
  FILTER ( LANG( ?positionLabel ) = "en" )
}
